title: Episode 179 - Shaahin Cheyene: Making Billions Selling Legal Ecstacy
description:
Show Notes: 

In this episode, I interview Shaahin Cheyene, pill pusher, vape pioneer and Amazon expert, who made a billion dollars selling herbal ecstacy in the 1990's and then leveraged Amazon to generate huge profits in the vaping space.

We discuss:

What made a 15 year old kid so ambitious to make so much money selling drugs?
Is corporate culture dead? Does everyone need to start their own business?
Is there still hope for the rags to riches path to millions?
How he started the vaping industry...
How he became an Amazon e-commerce expert...
How to create recurring revenue and start your own business, even if you don't have a product or idea...
Links:
Free 1-Hour course, email Shaahin drkzess@gmial.com and mention "Leverage or Robbie Kramer" 
fbasellercourse.com
